targets.query: SELECT mean(total) as total, mean(used) as used, mean(cached) as cached, mean(free) as free, mean(buffered) as buffered  FROM "mem" WHERE host =~ /$server$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host ORDER BY asc

SELECT mean(usage_user) as "user", mean(usage_system) as "system", mean(usage_softirq) as "softirq", mean(usage_steal) as "steal", mean(usage_nice) as "nice", mean(usage_irq) as "irq", mean(usage_iowait) as "iowait", mean(usage_guest) as "guest", mean(usage_guest_nice) as "guest_nice"  FROM "cpu" WHERE "host" =~ /$server$/ and cpu = 'cpu-total' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), *
SELECT mean(total) AS "total", mean(used) as "used" FROM "disk" WHERE "host" =~ /$server$/ AND "path" =~ /^$mountpoint$/AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "host", "path"
SELECT last("n_images") FROM "docker" WHERE ("engine_host" =~ /^$dockerhost$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("n_containers") FROM "docker" WHERE ("engine_host" =~ /^$dockerhost$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT distinct("container_id") AS "Container ID" FROM "docker_container_blkio" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "container_image",  "container_version", "container_status"
